===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
In its current form, a {{Han compound|ls=psc|nocap=1|亢|土|c1=p|c2=s|t2=soil}}. Early forms appear to be {{lang|zh|阬}}.

===Etymology 1===
Possibly related to {{och-l|空|empty; space; air}}, though the function of the ''*-r-'' in the Old Chinese reconstruction is unclear and its presence thus problematic (STEDT).

